                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18450303-713-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18450303-713-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18450303-713-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp>for embezzling the sum of 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 13<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the monies of his master, <persName id="t18450303-name-499" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450303-name-499" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450303-name-499" type="surname" value="COCKER"></interp>
